(Biandu)

216
00:13:08,140 --> 00:13:11,180
(Aula Kunning)

217
00:13:11,780 --> 00:13:14,180
(Putra Mahkota,
Zhao Xiaoze)

218
00:13:15,320 --> 00:13:17,750
Nona Shen menyerahkan catatan
ketika masuk istana hari ini.

219
00:13:17,800 --> 00:13:19,400
(Pengawas Aula Kunning, Wang Xian)

220
00:13:19,520 --> 00:13:21,039
Katanya ingin bertemu Kaisar.

221
00:13:22,919 --> 00:13:24,960
Sudah berapa kali menyerahkan
dalam sebulan ini.

